cobbler
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a sheep with coarse, grimy wool that is difficult to shear and can blunt cutters and combs.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
